Location: Your Apartment
(link:"Look around")[A compact living space, about 12 by 18 feet, clearly designed to hold the most accomodation, (kitchen, bathroom, sleeping area) in the most efficient space possible. It's decorated with ''//TK//'' but it isn't enough to get rid of the mass produced reality of the space. There is no natural light.&lt;br&gt;]
